{"tid":587210,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[311連登推薦名單]九龍西蔡東洲 香港島任亮憲 新界東黃成智","createTime":"2018-03-10T08:38:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-11T03:59:12.000Z","uid":29804,"like":0,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c12392a5b48ba4ac0d74eaccd5650b66ad6eff88","tid":587210,"uid":29804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T08:38:40.000Z","msg":"九龍西<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/10/163053_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F10%2F163053_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=71799a2c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n蔡東洲<br />\n香港理工大學物理治療學(榮譽)理學士<br />\n中山大學物理治療針灸文憑<br />\n香港理工大學管理學理學碩士（公營機構管理）<br />\n<br />\n為社會上的基層和弱勢社群服務<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港島<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/fr/cp0/e15/q65/26165461_1479131955536745_1710071803390421553_n.png.jpg?oh=0c2f3d66e18888c4d4c13aeb662f925a&amp;oe=5B05968D\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Ffr%2Fcp0%2Fe15%2Fq65%2F26165461_1479131955536745_1710071803390421553_n.png.jpg%3Foh%3D0c2f3d66e18888c4d4c13aeb662f925a%26oe%3D5B05968D&h=25639e4d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n任亮憲<br />\n伊利諾大學財經系學士<br />\n前社民連成員<br />\n前人民力量成員<br />\n<br />\n保兩制 拼經濟 任亮憲 創出路<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n新界東<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t31.0-8/fr/cp0/e15/q65/27023872_1422284821231382_2935818885498007884_o.jpg?efg=eyJpIjoibyJ9&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;oh=84a28851a3e33ef000b543ef0bcd90b2&amp;oe=5B033420\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft31.0-8%2Ffr%2Fcp0%2Fe15%2Fq65%2F27023872_1422284821231382_2935818885498007884_o.jpg%3Fefg%3DeyJpIjoibyJ9%26_nc_ad%3Dz-m%26_nc_cid%3D0%26oh%3D84a28851a3e33ef000b543ef0bcd90b2%26oe%3D5B033420&h=96759a18&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n黃成